<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Successful Admission Application Submission - FUUAST Islamabad</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 20px;
            background:
                linear-gradient(45deg, #ffffff 25%, transparent 25%) 0 0,
                linear-gradient(-45deg, #ffffff 25%, transparent 25%) 0 0;
            background-size: 20px 20px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .header h2 {
            margin: 10px 0 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: normal;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
        }
        @("@")media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                width: 100% !important;
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Admission Application Submitted Successfully</h1>
            <h2>Federal Urdu University of Arts, Sciences & Technology, Islamabad</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear @Model.ApplicantName,</p>
            <p>We are pleased to confirm that your admission application to FUUAST Islamabad has been successfully submitted.</p>
            <p>Here are the details of your submission:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Application ID: @Model.ApplicationFormId</li>
                <li>Date Submitted: @Model.SubmissionDate</li>
            </ul>

            <p>If you have any questions or need to update your application, please don't hesitate to contact our admissions office at admissions@fuuastisb.edu.pk or call us at 051-9252860-64 Between 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM.</p>
            <p>Thank you for choosing FUUAST Islamabad for your higher education. We wish you the best of luck with your application!</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>Admissions Office<br>FUUAST Islamabad</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
            <p>© 2024 Federal Urdu University of Arts, Sciences & Technology, Islamabad. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>